@End Implementation

@Performance_Hints
Time: O(1).
@End Performance_Hints

@Security_Scope
Bounds-checked.
@End Security_Scope
Process called "tuple_get_6" takes tup as Integer returns Integer:
    Return proc tuple_get with tup, 6
